description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Caribbean Barbados
-Small boat in the evening sun
-Sunset over Africa
-Cottage on the South Pacific
-Mt.Fuji is reflected in a lake
-Sunset view of Miyajima, Japan
-Maldivian Sea
-At the resort pool
-Castle ruins in Scotland
-Dog at the mediterranean sea
name: Sunset
